                  </persName>
            , I believe to be his writing, and I believe the body of the account, and the body of the certificate to be his writing, except the names, which do not purport to be his. I know the Captain's hand-writing, 
               <persName id="t18210411-72-person851">
                  William 
                  Furlong Wise
