               <persName id="t18210411-72-person854">
                  Luke 
                  Bell
               <interp inst="t18210411-72-person854" type="surname" value="Bell"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-72-person854" type="given" value="Luke"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-72-person854" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , he was carpenter of the Spartan. I have frequently seen him write, I believe neither of the signatures in the columns to be his.</p>
               <p>Q. Was 
               <persName id="t18210411-72-person855">
                  Nicholas 
                  Hede
               <interp inst="t18210411-72-person855" type="surname" value="Hede"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-72-person855" type="given" value="Nicholas"></interp>
